OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777395954
OL,3,CCannabis gang who 'smiled' alongside
OL,4,C#1m haul jailed
OL,6,FA drugs gang who posed for photos in
OL,7,Ffront of a huge cannabis farm have
OL,8,Fbeen jailed after police discovered a
OL,9,Fmassive "sophisticated" factory inside
OL,10,Fan industrial unit.
OL,12,FIndrid Hysembelli, 26, Xhoi Kasaj, 30,
OL,13,Fand Romeo Tosca, 26, were sentenced to
OL,14,Fa combined total of eight years and
OL,15,Fsix months behind bars after being
OL,16,Fconvicted of the production of Class B
OL,17,Fdrugs at Minshull Street Crown Court.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
