OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777395954
OL,3,CCannabis gang who 'smiled' alongside
OL,4,C#1m haul jailed
OL,6,FThe sentencing follows a raid in the
OL,7,Fearly hours of 17 June 2025, where
OL,8,Fofficers from Greater Manchester
OL,9,FPolice forced entry into a "heavily
OL,10,Fsecure" building on Bilsley Street, in
OL,11,FOldham.
OL,13,FOnce inside, specialist officers
OL,14,Funcovered a huge cannabis cultivation
OL,15,Fsetup. In total, 889 cannabis plants
OL,16,Fwere seized, with a potential street
OL,17,Fvalue estimated at #986,800.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777395954
OL,3,CCannabis gang who 'smiled' alongside
OL,4,C#1m haul jailed
OL,6,FHysembelli, Kasaj and Tosca, who are
OL,7,Fall of Albanian decent, were found
OL,8,Fhiding in the loft space, where they
OL,9,Fwere subsequently arrested.
OL,11,FThe men were living in "extremely
OL,12,Fpoor" conditions, police say, with
OL,13,Ffour cramped bunk beds, a basic
OL,14,Fkitchen area with a fridge and cooker,
OL,15,Fand a TV displaying live CCTV feeds
OL,16,Ffrom the building's perimeter.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777395954
OL,3,CCannabis gang who 'smiled' alongside
OL,4,C#1m haul jailed
OL,6,FDetectives also confirmed that the
OL,7,Fgang had bypassed the electricity
OL,8,Fsupply, connecting directly to the
OL,9,Fmains to power the industrial-grade
OL,10,Fheating and lighting equipment
OL,11,Frequired for the farm.
OL,13,FHysembelli received the longest
OL,14,Fsentence of three years and seven
OL,15,Fmonths, with Tosca and Kasaj sentenced
OL,16,Fto two years and eight months, and two
OL,17,Fyears and three months respectively.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777395954
OL,3,CCannabis gang who 'smiled' alongside
OL,4,C#1m haul jailed
OL,6,FSpeaking after the sentencing,
OL,7,FDetective Constable Christopher Brown,
OL,8,Ffrom GMP's Oldham Division, warned
OL,9,Fthat such operations are a "serious
OL,10,Frisk" to the public.
OL,12,F"Drug dealing is not a victimless
OL,13,Fcrime. It is closely linked to violent
OL,14,Fgang activity and the exploitation of
OL,15,Fvulnerable people - serious issues
OL,16,Fthat impact communities across Greater
OL,17,FManchester," DC Brown said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777395954
OL,3,CCannabis gang who 'smiled' alongside
OL,4,C#1m haul jailed
OL,6,F"These sentences reflect the
OL,7,Fseriousness of the offence and send a
OL,8,Fclear message that those involved in
OL,9,Fthe production and supply of illegal
OL,10,Fdrugs will be identified, arrested and
OL,11,Fbrought before the courts."
OL,13,FThe raid was part of an ongoing
OL,14,Fregional crackdown on organised drug
OL,15,Fproduction. Police have urged anyone
OL,16,Fwith information regarding local drug
OL,17,Fcultivation to contact them or reach
OL,18,Fout to Crimestoppers anonymously
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
